Use case 4 : Build - > Ship : Build a custom image contains CENTS OS, JDK 1.7 and Tomcat 7
            a. Log into the terminal show the installation of the utilities 
            b. docker tag the build
            c. docker tag
            d. docker login and creds stored in WINDOWS C:\Users\<username>\.docker\config.json and in MAC/UNIX in ~/.docker
            e. docker push
                        
Use case 5 : Docker create another image with the war file using the image created in usecase 4
            a. Create another image from the image in Use case 4
            b. Run a container, login to the container, change some setting
            c. docker commit a container as an image
            d. docker push

Use case 6 : Continuous integration with Git and Docker.

Use case 7 : Introduction to docker compose and how you can run compose to run docker machines
Use case 8 : Introduction to docker swarm and how to run clusters using docker